Everything revolves around a sprint, all actions and reactions of the team effects the sprint. 

A sprint is nothing but fixed amount of days in which a team decides to build and/or fix things. i,e at the end of the sprint the product team(PM + Engg + QA + DevOps + etc)
must do a production release of tasks which add value to the customer and the business. Value addition can be bigor small depeding upon the tasks, team strength, team expertise etc. 

Generally, a sprint is of 2 weeks time. Sometimes, teams also run a speed sprint of lesser duration of say 1 week as well. But generally it is 2 weeks. 

